ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I recommend anyone who is interested in trade and political economy to take this course. Before taking this class, I was interested in political economy, not trade. However, after taking this course, I got an overview of trade theory and enjoyed it very much.
I would absolutely recommend the course to a fellow student interested in either trade policy, political economy or especially both.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: Through this course I was able to refine my interest in certain aspects of trade policy and political economy, which I found very useful - perhaps not for my dissertation or current research but I hope for other research during my career.
